---
title: Roast Root Veggie Medley with Goat Cheese, Candied Pecans & Dill
description: A feast for the eyes as well as the stomach, this medley is a true celebration of the sweet nuttiness that can be found in a savoury dish. Between kumara and beetroot, goat cheese and crunchy candied pecans, you won’t be able to decide what to eat first!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/5ba98725ae08b51e75389ab2-a03671cf.jpg
